{"tid":973014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"平時見開冇乜感覺，但啱啱收工坐巴士果陣認真咁望過維港，原來真係好靚","createTime":"2019-01-07T21:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T19:40:15.000Z","uid":59501,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c0b19dc1f55293f4e795a9536732c0534c77edc","tid":973014,"uid":59501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:20:36.000Z","msg":"係半夜冇乜燈光反而有種靜態美<br />\n忍唔住定哂神咁望<br />\n然後先發覺有好多地方已經唔同左<br />\n唔經唔覺原來香港真係變左好多<br />\n<br />\n然後慢慢巴士駛到郵輪碼頭附近<br />\n望見到果條頭上面有口釘既蟲<br />\n再諗起呢十幾二十年係香港發生既野<br />\n口心突然沉左一下<br />\n有種唔識形容既絕望感湧出黎<br />\n究竟香港點解會由一個充滿希望既地方變成今時今日咁絕望<br />\n<br />\n咁啱耳機忽然開始播美麗新香港<br />\n聽下聽下對面海既風景忽然間越來越濛<br />\n濛到我忍唔住合埋對眼<br />\n直到落車之前個站<br />\n我都再冇打開過隻眼<br />\n<br />\n依家回想返<br />\n我果刻就好似大部份香港人咁<br />\n面對眼前發現緊既問題都視而不見選擇逃避<br />\n以為合埋眼唔睇唔望就唔會影響到自己<br />\n去到最後先知道原來果d最值得珍惜既熟悉風景已經一去不返"},{"pid":"5a494dceac6929e8044551b338f07b6f1225e753","tid":973014,"uid":59501,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:31:19.000Z","msg":"今晚明明冇平時咁忙<br />\n但唔知點解無論身心都好似比平時更加攰咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff8f690e28d80f6f1907047f2b7cde40a75005f","tid":973014,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:36:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48ef1c910ee2b7d931b7a99bd3aff5d30026da23","tid":973014,"uid":59501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:36:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aTLFonM32B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaTLFonM32B4&d=0g%2Bqkt12DDtyN51eMBLZFP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fa841fd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aTLFonM32B4</a><br />\n早幾年睇直播果陣仲覺得點解唱歌走哂音都可以上台表演<br />\n睇到一半就轉左台<br />\n<br />\n依家已經變左最常聽既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54a716e4327b28271db18b00e298821de5672ab","tid":973014,"uid":59501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eff8f690e28d80f6f1907047f2b7cde40a75005f","tid":973014,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:36:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:39:58.000Z","msg":"啟德"},{"pid":"9e13669995544606a4f53e39045e6e58322be70e","tid":973014,"uid":89999,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T21:44:07.000Z","msg":"一路讀篇文，我已經分唔到mon上面既係窗外既雨粉定係我既淚水"},{"pid":"b8189632cb7a2f9e24e21d51403fdda55cd32540","tid":973014,"uid":214997,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T22:20:24.000Z","msg":"聽my little airport最深刻一段歌詞<br />\n<br />\n你上年返鄉下之後 覺得人應該留係城市<br />\n我話 香港有啲年輕人開始學種田<br />\n你話 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港咁繁榮 點解會有人學種田</span><br />\n-廣州足浴一夜"},{"pid":"2cb3e3091a3dfd50de4b9497ab3836d472265b78","tid":973014,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T22:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c95455d0381cd1b535ef529f0570f90f54d1a72","tid":973014,"uid":147226,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T22:50:30.000Z","msg":"已經唔靚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 維港兩岸啲大招牌變晒支那公司，設計好無品味"},{"pid":"87854e0f44b92fa4e6fee66a20a5099272d3bc9f","tid":973014,"uid":59501,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c95455d0381cd1b535ef529f0570f90f54d1a72","tid":973014,"uid":147226,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T22:50:30.000Z","msg":"已經唔靚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 維港兩岸啲大招牌變晒支那公司，設計好無品味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"都啱，睇返舊戲入面既維港真係靚過依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6634342d0490616e33c08ff009d3583dd2e567","tid":973014,"uid":219216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T14:54:10.